data.description: Come one Come all to see this beautiful, immaculately well-kept home. This home features elegant hardwood floors, it is located in the tranquil neighborhood of Liberty Lakes. This well-maintained residence offers three bedrooms and two baths, providing comfortable living space for its occupants. The interior features a spacious layout with an open-concept design that creates a seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it perfect for both everyday living and entertaining. The primary bedroom has a walk-in closet and the primary bath.   The home has a new roof installed in 2023 and a new HVAC unit in 2022. The attic is equipped with a Radiant Berrier used for regulating interior climate, as well as the back door is equipped with Energy energy-efficient berrier to control the climate in the kitchen.  The utility room is located inside of the home.  This home is a must-see!
